[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":732},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpython\u002F20210921\u002F473845764\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpython\u002F20210921\u002F473845764\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpython\u002F20210921\u002F473845764\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpython\u002F20210921\u002F473845764\u002F":708,"related:\u002Fpython\u002F20210921\u002F473845764\u002F":717},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F21\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-20-csv\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":691,"date":692,"description":18,"extension":693,"lang":694,"meta":695,"navigation":385,"path":696,"readingMinutes":697,"seo":698,"standalone":699,"stem":700,"tags":701,"tldr":705,"updated":705,"url":706,"__hash__":707},"content\u002F從 JavaScript 角度學 Python\u002F從-JavaScript-角度學-Python-20-CSV.md","從 JavaScript 角度學 Python(20) - CSV","473845764",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":683},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,36,39,63,71,83,86,92,95,98,104,108,111,130,133,139,142,145,151,154,165,170,178,181,184,212,215,224,227,234,273,284,290,306,309,320,326,329,360,366,403,409,412,418,422,425,428,452,463,485,492,519,522,544,547,616,630,633,636,639,673,679],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"前一章節簡單的聊了一下 JSON 之後，接下來我想額外補充一個關於 CSV 檔案處理的部分，而 CSV 通常在批次匯入的時候會很常看到，所以就特別拉一篇來聊聊。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"who-is-csv","who is CSV",[16,24,25],{},"通常看到 CSV 檔案的時候，大多人會覺得它是一個 Excel 或是 Google 試算表也不爲過，畢竟通常我們開啟 CSV 就是使用這幾種軟體去打開，我以前還以為 CSV 就是 Excel，還傻傻的問說 CSV 檔該怎麼打開。",[16,27,28],{},"應該是我太笨了吧？對吧？還是你也跟我一樣一開始以為 CSV 只是單純的 Excel 格式的一種呢？下面留言給我吧，讓我知道我不孤單。",[16,30,31],{},[32,33],"img",{"alt":34,"src":35},"猶豫自己該不該承認","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F1631631336586.png",[16,37,38],{},"好，那麼什麼是 CSV 呢？CSV 是 Comma-Separated Values 的縮寫(我破英文覺得難唸)，中文名稱是「逗號分隔值」，顧名思義就是使用逗號去做分隔每一個值的，通常第一排會是欄位名稱：",[40,41,46],"pre",{"className":42,"code":43,"language":44,"meta":45,"style":45},"language-csv shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","name,title,url\nray,是 Ray 不是 Array,https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F\n","csv","",[47,48,49,57],"code",{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,51,54],"span",{"class":52,"line":53},"line",1,[50,55,56],{},"name,title,url\n",[50,58,60],{"class":52,"line":59},2,[50,61,62],{},"ray,是 Ray 不是 Array,https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F\n",[16,64,65,66,70],{},"因此其實你使用 .txt 來撰寫也是可以達到相同效果，畢竟 CSV 就是一個",[67,68,69],"strong",{},"純文字","的檔案，因此你可以嘗試建立一個純文字檔案，然後寫入下方內容：",[40,72,73],{"className":42,"code":43,"language":44,"meta":45,"style":45},[47,74,75,79],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,76,77],{"class":52,"line":53},[50,78,56],{},[50,80,81],{"class":52,"line":59},[50,82,62],{},[16,84,85],{},"接下來存檔！再將副檔名改成 .csv，在去打開，你會發現是可以正常運作的，是不是超簡單的~",[16,87,88],{},[32,89],{"alt":90,"src":91},"簡單到兔牙都出來了","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F1631672494.png",[16,93,94],{},"因此如果你有使用一些批量匯入的服務，你也可以發現大多都是支援 .csv 與 .txt 哩~",[16,96,97],{},"那麼為什麼要特別講到 CSV 呢？就如同前面所言，許多系統都會支援 .csv 批次匯入，甚至你也可以看到一些爬蟲爬完資料之後就轉換成 CSV 格式，然後再上傳到自己的分析系統，所以好 CSV 不了解一下怎麼在 Python 中如何使用嗎？",[16,99,100],{},[32,101],{"alt":102,"src":103},"好 CSV 不學嗎","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F1631710638550.png",[12,105,107],{"id":106},"讀取-csv","讀取 CSV",[16,109,110],{},"那麼首先我們先學如何讀取 CSV 當作起手式，因此我這邊有準備有一個簡易版的 .csv 檔，分別欄位是名字、標題與網址：",[40,112,114],{"className":42,"code":113,"language":44,"meta":45,"style":45},"name,title,url\nray,是 Ray 不是 Array,https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F\nray,第-13-屆-iT邦幫忙鐵人賽,https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Ftags\u002F第-13-屆-iT邦幫忙鐵人賽\u002F\n",[47,115,116,120,124],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,117,118],{"class":52,"line":53},[50,119,56],{},[50,121,122],{"class":52,"line":59},[50,123,62],{},[50,125,127],{"class":52,"line":126},3,[50,128,129],{},"ray,第-13-屆-iT邦幫忙鐵人賽,https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Ftags\u002F第-13-屆-iT邦幫忙鐵人賽\u002F\n",[16,131,132],{},"蛤？你問我範例的 .csv 哪裡下載？我剛剛不是已經教你怎麼建立 csv 了嗎？",[16,134,135],{},[32,136],{"alt":137,"src":138},"給我檔案","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F1631711248099.png",[16,140,141],{},"簡單來講，你先建立一個 .txt 的文字檔案，然後填入我上面給的內容，再將副檔名改成 .csv 就可以囉。",[16,143,144],{},"那麼當你建立好後使用 Excel 或是 Google 試算表打開會像這樣子呈現：",[16,146,147],{},[32,148],{"alt":149,"src":150},"Google 試算表","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-08-08%2015.27.43.png",[16,152,153],{},"題外話一下你可以嘗試將 .csv 檔案拖進 VSCode 中，這樣也可以打開來看的。",[16,155,156,157,164],{},"但是如果你覺得一推逗號很難看的話，也可以替 VSCode 安裝 ",[158,159,163],"a",{"href":160,"rel":161},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=GrapeCity.gc-excelviewer",[162],"nofollow","Excel Viewer"," 套件來觀看 csv 檔：",[16,166,167],{},[32,168],{"alt":163,"src":169},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-08-08%2015.35.35.png",[16,171,172,173,177],{},"(這邊也稍微讓我置入性行銷一下，如果你想知道更多套件的話，可以閱讀這一篇 ",[158,174,176],{"href":175},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20191212\u002F2147775133\u002F","Visual Studio Code(VSCode) 必備實用套件","。)",[16,179,180],{},"稍微扯遠了，讓我們回到 Python 中，接下來由於要讀取 CSV 檔案所以我們必須引入 CSV 模組，概念就跟使用 JSON 的時候一樣。",[16,182,183],{},"但是在引入之前我們可以先嘗試打開 .csv 檔案：",[40,185,189],{"className":186,"code":187,"language":188,"meta":45,"style":45},"language-py shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","f = open('example.csv', 'r')\nread = f.read()\nf.close()\nprint(read)\n","py",[47,190,191,196,201,206],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,192,193],{"class":52,"line":53},[50,194,195],{},"f = open('example.csv', 'r')\n",[50,197,198],{"class":52,"line":59},[50,199,200],{},"read = f.read()\n",[50,202,203],{"class":52,"line":126},[50,204,205],{},"f.close()\n",[50,207,209],{"class":52,"line":208},4,[50,210,211],{},"print(read)\n",[16,213,214],{},"基本上我們可以知道是可以正常運作的，但是如果你想要取值的話就會無法正常取值：",[40,216,218],{"className":186,"code":217,"language":188,"meta":45,"style":45},"print(read['name']) # TypeError: string indices must be integers\n",[47,219,220],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,221,222],{"class":52,"line":53},[50,223,217],{},[16,225,226],{},"畢竟概念就跟 JSON 章節的狀況是一樣的。",[16,228,229,230,233],{},"哦！順道提一下，在 Node.js 開發時也是需要引入 CSV 相關套件的，例如...",[47,231,232],{},"csv-parse","：",[40,235,239],{"className":236,"code":237,"language":238,"meta":45,"style":45},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","var csvParse = require('csv-parse');\n...\n","js",[47,240,241,268],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,242,243,247,251,254,258,261,265],{"class":52,"line":53},[50,244,246],{"class":245},"sWyjQ","var",[50,248,250],{"class":249},"sMAXC"," csvParse ",[50,252,253],{"class":245},"=",[50,255,257],{"class":256},"sj_SG"," require",[50,259,260],{"class":249},"(",[50,262,264],{"class":263},"sTRMh","'csv-parse'",[50,266,267],{"class":249},");\n",[50,269,270],{"class":52,"line":59},[50,271,272],{"class":245},"...\n",[16,274,275,276,279,280,283],{},"因此我們就會需要借助 CSV 模組的方法來幫我們正確的讀取轉換 .csv 資料，而讀取的函式是 ",[47,277,278],{},"reader()","，如果想要正確的取出資料的話，就必須使用 ",[47,281,282],{},"for in"," 迴圈。",[16,285,286,287,289],{},"疑？為什麼要用 ",[47,288,282],{}," 呢？主要原因是 CSV 模組在處理時，它會將逗號結尾最後一個元素的作為一個陣列的終點，什麼意思呢？例如剛剛的範例：",[40,291,292],{"className":42,"code":113,"language":44,"meta":45,"style":45},[47,293,294,298,302],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,295,296],{"class":52,"line":53},[50,297,56],{},[50,299,300],{"class":52,"line":59},[50,301,62],{},[50,303,304],{"class":52,"line":126},[50,305,129],{},[16,307,308],{},"雖然我前面是這樣講，但是實際上你輸出的話會看到一串詭異的東西：",[40,310,314],{"className":311,"code":312,"language":313,"meta":45,"style":45},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\u003C_csv.reader object at 0x1021b7660>\n","cmd",[47,315,316],{"__ignoreMap":45},[50,317,31